# Testing and CI

Run all checks with **`make ci`** (lint, PHPCS, PHPStan, PHPUnit) — inside the dev container only; never assume host `composer`/`php`. Tool config lives in `tests/` (`phpunit.xml`, `phpstan.neon`, `phpcs.xml`, `rector.php`) — keep it there.

Full command reference: **[docs/development.md](../../docs/development.md)**. Standards: **[AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md)**.
